00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Cooking in water

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Simply immerse the pieces of celery in boiling water with a pinch of salt.  
Allow about 5 minutes to blanch them. 
Or 10 minutes to cook completely. 

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:34.000
Drain, then drop into a bowl of ice water. 

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:42.000
